{"tid":1579661,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"新移民哭訴中共、港共暴政","createTime":"2019-09-18T16:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T14:20:31.000Z","uid":82228,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d895c582cc0f4d5b48b0e333a4e95da6b16b7221","tid":1579661,"uid":82228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:20:37.000Z","msg":"片中女士帶著鄉音說粵語，表示自己是香港新移民。她說移民到香港，因為對自己國家無信心。憶述自己和朋友在內地遇到的慘況時淚聲俱下，表示<span style=\"color: red;\">共產黨「咩都做得出」</span>。她亦想向香港人說，家中曾經當軍人，六十多歲的父親和母親也支持香港人，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">並呼籲香港人多發文宣告訴內地人香港的真相！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AvbtW7cNzoI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAvbtW7cNzoI&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=11e35987\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AvbtW7cNzoI</a>"},{"pid":"b7c4106951d8304a3e229ae7c1f504c2e76a18ed","tid":1579661,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"518a4c1bff67e3e70ca17692aed186b8641049dc","tid":1579661,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:21:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66ac4d632dab67eb5641ee2b1ebd76099df5b7aa","tid":1579661,"uid":82228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:21:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84a2c9676a50b9b6bddfb1ba93c438c7a65152df","tid":1579661,"uid":82228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"848e683429566782811075592867987a4d2fe3fa","tid":1579661,"uid":82228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:24:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63ce9fa56065fb812481202acf4ceafd8760cd2a","tid":1579661,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:24:25.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東道主</strong></span></span>倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>10.1國殤</strong></span>打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！<br />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！</strong></span><br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c0d976439d8e256cca286fd74bbb44451eb1e0e","tid":1579661,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:24:32.000Z","msg":"有野想捐可以FB/TG搵我地香港自由之書阿<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">想支持某間發國難財的五金鋪,但又唔方便親自落去買水買衫? 入黎喇</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1573714/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1573714/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nFB: 國難五金, 香港自由之書<br />\n<br />\n真係無事邊會咁咁多人沖落黎 貪住得細咩"},{"pid":"7775303991a3b7b17a66c4c22c4af4845d928c31","tid":1579661,"uid":82228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:36:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5dbaa9c5e8402e0921a2b53dc8359be1a5057a64","tid":1579661,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:40:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7129534eaa0f0de27fcfeb7c2acc2adea0781701","tid":1579661,"uid":88578,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:52:04.000Z","msg":"屌你，聽到我流眼水。<br />\n手足，新移民不是罪，只要愛港，就係我地嘅手足"},{"pid":"f202c29b9b37f66e69b637295249dac0d8151cd7","tid":1579661,"uid":56790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:55:37.000Z","msg":"有無文字版？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />己經好盡力聽"},{"pid":"4cb183c84b014d7666d3de940ff84d843daeedb2","tid":15796